AAAA&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjRhNzKx4DnAhUcBGMBHYs1A24Q0EAwFnoECAwQIw\">Antiviral drug</a></li><li>Reduces viruses&#39; ability to replicate.</li></ul>'),
